structure_for_AI_to_understand: ProgramsJSON: Root object with programs array and optional metadata (sources, lastUpdated)
Program: Contains projectCode (7-digit string), name (string), and programDescriptions array
ProgramDescription: Contains description (string) and source (string or array of strings)
Project Codes: 7-digit identifiers as strings - either direct 7-digit codes or 4-digit program codes with '000' appended
Data Sources: Extracted from budget text files and vendor transaction CSV files
Multiple Descriptions: Programs can have multiple descriptions from different sources with source tracking
Processing: New programs added when found, existing programs get additional descriptions from new sources
Source Tracking: Each description tracks which budget file or vendor CSV it came from
